Accepted Inputs:
  -It will follow directly the cursor's position.
  
Known Bugs:
  -Sometimes the ball gets stuck near vertical edges of the app.
  -The track of the mouse isn't necesarrily fluid.

Highlighted Features:
  -The more bricks you destroy, the faster the ball will be
  -The speed from the ball remains from the previous level if you win
